Quite apart from her singing, she was much in the news in the Spring of 1916, becaus eher husband was arrested and charged with plotting to blow up the Welland Canal.  See, for example, the NYT of March 31, 1916
  select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F10E13FE3A5B17738DDDA80B94DB405B868DF1D3
&quot;GADSKI'S HUSBAND ARRESTED IN PLOT TO BLOW UP CANAL; Capt. Tauscher, Krupp Agent, Seized as Conspirator to Wreck Welland Waterway. DATES BACK TO AUGUST, '14 Von der Goltz Gave Evidence Involving von Papen, Which Led to Capture. RAID THROUGH PRIVATE DOOR Government Holds Him in $25,000 Bail -- Admits Activity, but Denies the Charge. GADSKI'S HUSBAND ARRESTED IN PLOT&quot;
